resources.string: آپ کا پیغام یہاں ٹائپ کریں
CloudKibo کریش ہو گیا! رپورٹ ڈویلپر کی طرف بھیجا گیا ہے.
آپ نے کامیابی سے گروپ چھوڑ دیا

KiboChat is a next generation communication technology. It’s intuitive, cost effective, and rich with functionality. It can be used both for internal and external communications. It provides integrated and unified voice, video, and data communication across web. KiboChat lets you invite your friend with a click of a button into a call. Don’t get tied down to a clumsy keypad and cryptic codes to control and manage your calls. KiboChat also allows you to invite multiple people to join the Web meeting without installing any complex software. All they need to do is visit a URL and join the meeting. KiboChat uses VP8 codec, which allows efficient use of bandwidth estimation for better video quality. VP8 adaptable technology allows you have HD quality. It also includes components to conceal pack loss and clean up noisy images. KiboChat stunning HD audio quality lets you experience the full, glorious range of the human voice. Wideband and Narrowband PSTN codec are supported. KiboChat lets you share your weekly project status, share your weekly sales slides, collect feedback on the latest design rendering, and makes sharing a screen easy as clicking the “Share Screen” button. KiboChat makes it simple for you or anyone in your call to instantly share notes, documents, videos, or any other file. File transfer is highly secured. All file transfers are peer to peer with 128 Bit encryption. Current email systems normally limit your attachments to 25MB and multiple copies of your files are left on the mail servers. Downloading, installing, and updating plugins can be complex, error prone, and annoying. With KiboChat you are able to join the call straight from your browser without any need to download and install client software. Plugins can be difficult to deploy, debug, troubleshoot, test and maintain and may require licensing and integration with complex, expensive technology. KiboChat connects you to social network services like Facebook, Google, and Microsoft. You can connect and import your friends from these social networks. KiboChat is based on modern Web technology like Nodejs, Angularjs, Socket.io, WebRTC etc, thus it is highly scalable. Also as most of the communication is Peer to Peer the need for a large and complex server platform is minimized resulting in a very cost effective solution. KiboChat is highly secured as all communication is 128 Bit encrypted and the base technology uses Peer to Peer communication between two end points. No customer content audio, video, or files are stored on the central server.

Backup your messages and media to Google Drive. You can restore them when you reinstall KiboChat. Your messages and media will also back up to your phone\'s internal storage. Media and messages you back up are not protected by KiboChat end-to-end encryption while in Google Drive.
